<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENBP70A7204A11" svcinfotypenbr = "06" svcinfoqualnbr = "03">
<title>
During A/C compressor operation, a rumbling noise is heard as to engine speed increases
</title>
<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A7204004001">
<title>
Abnormal Noise from A/C Compressor
</title>
<diag type = "condition">
<condition>
<ptxt>
During A/C compressor operation, a rumbling noise is heard as to engine speed increases
</ptxt>
</condition>
<ps>
<ptxt>
Inadequate clearance in scroll area
</ptxt>
</ps>
<action>
<ptxt>
Replace A/C compressor. 
